The '''asaari tree''' was a [[Sentience/Legends|non-sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of tree which grew in the vast [[Asaari woods|forests]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bimmisaari/Legends|Bimmisaari]]. While they were not capable of moving from their rooted position, the tree was able to move its leafy branches of its own accord.<ref name="HESB" />

